SubjectAgreement on Social Security between Canada and the Republic of Albania ** Entry into Force **
PrecisOrder declaring the ENTRY INTO FORCE of the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF ALBANIA, signed at Ottawa on April 30, 2019, on the first day of the fourth month after each party has notified the other by the exchange of diplomatic notes that it has completed the internal legal procedures necessary for the entry into force of this Agreement.
